n >= &0
|- undef_array_at (to_pre,Tchar,n) |--
   fact (&0 <= n) **
   fact (&0 <= &0) **
   undef_array_at (to_pre + &0 * sizeof Tchar,Tchar,n - &0)

|- forall x ty n.
       n > &0
       ==> (undef_array_at (x,ty,n) -|-
            undef_data_at (x,ty) ** undef_array_at (x + sizeof ty,ty,n - &1))

|- len - i > &0
   ==> (undef_array_at (to + i * sizeof Tchar,Tchar,len - i) -|-
        undef_data_at (to + i * sizeof Tchar,Tchar) **
        undef_array_at
        ((to + i * sizeof Tchar) + sizeof Tchar,Tchar,len - i - &1))

|- len - i > &0
   ==> (undef_array_at (to + i * sizeof Tchar,Tchar,len - i) |--
        undef_data_at (to + i * sizeof Tchar,Tchar) **
        undef_array_at
        ((to + i * sizeof Tchar) + sizeof Tchar,Tchar,len - i - &1))

|- (exists i_v.
        fact (n >= &0) **
        fact (i_v <= n) **
        fact (&0 <= i_v) **
        fact (i < len) **
        data_at (& i"

exists i_v.
    fact (i_v < n) **
    fact (&0 <= i_v) **
    fact (i_v <= n) **
    fact (n >= &0) **
    data_at (& i"

|- i_v >= &0
   ==> (array_at (to_pre,Tchar,replicate (i_v,&0)) **
        data_at (to_pre + i_v * sizeof Tchar,Tchar,&0) |--
        array_at (to_pre,Tchar,replicate (i_v + &1,&0)))

|- (exists i_v.
        fact (n >= &0) **
        fact (&0 <= i_v) **
        fact (i_v < n) **
        fact (i_v <= n) **
        data_at (& i"

exists i_v.

    fact (&0 <= i_v) **
    fact (i_v <= n) **
    fact (n >= &0) **

n >= &0
|- fact (i_v < n) ** fact (&0 <= i_v) ** fact (i_v <= n) |--
   fact (i_v + &1 <= n) ** fact (&0 <= i_v + &1)

|- (exists i_v.
        fact (n >= &0) **
        fact (i_v <= n) **
        fact (&0 <= i_v) **
        fact (i_v < n) **

exists i_v.

i_v >= n, i_v <= n
|- i_v == n
|- fact (i_v >= n) ** fact (i_v <= n) |-- fact (i_v == n)

i_v == n
|- fact (&0 <= i_v) **
   fact (n >= &0) **
   data_at (& i"

|- fact (i_v >= n) **
   fact (&0 <= i_v) **
   fact (i_v <= n) **
   fact (n >= &0) **
